There’s this bakery right in front of me as I usually have my evening tea there when I’m back from work. getting back home after a long day’s work is tiring like everyone else, but I always look forward to it as I get to meet this guy. Every morning he walks (or escorts) me to the main road till I know my bus is here that takes me to work.
